(65, 7, 2, '따뜻한 저녁', 'PAGE', '구름 사이로 햇살이 비치자 모두가 미소지었습니다.', 'The last page of the book was missing, and no one knew why. Two old friends sat by the river and shared their stories. Nobody in town could explain where the music came from. The mountain path was steep, but the view was worth it. She found an old key hidden inside the wooden box.', NULL, '2025-05-30 19:42:42', '2025-06-17 19:42:42'),
(66, 7, 3, '다시 만난 날', 'PAGE', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page66/800/600', '2025-11-12 09:01:46', '2025-12-10 09:01:46'),
(67, 7, 4, '새로운 친구', 'PAGE', '오랜 기다림 끝에 반가운 소식이 도착했습니다.', 'Two old friends sat by the river and shared their stories. Nobody in town could explain where the music came from. Deep in the forest, something rustled quietly among the leaves. She found an old key hidden inside the wooden box.', NULL, '2025-03-27 23:40:21', '2025-03-28 23:40:21'),
(68, 7, 5, '숲으로', 'PAGE', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page68/800/600', '2026-02-10 08:29:01', '2026-02-10 08:29:01'),
(69, 7, 6, '첫 만남', 'PAGE', '달빛 아래에서 두 친구는 오래도록 이야기를 나누었습니다. 겨울이 지나고 봄이 오자 나무에 새싹이 돋았습니다. 아이는 손을 흔들며 친구에게 인사했습니다. 오랜 기다림 끝에 반가운 소식이 도착했습니다. 새로운 친구를 만난 순간, 마음이 두근거렸습니다.', 'She found an old key hidden inside the wooden box. The little village woke up slowly under the morning light. The old clock in the hallway had stopped ticking years ago. The garden was full of flowers no one remembered planting. A warm cup of tea waited for him on the table.', NULL, '2025-06-21 02:17:05', '2025-07-05 02:17:05'),
(70, 7, 7, '함께한 하루', 'PAGE', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page70/800/600', '2026-01-16 16:00:56', '2026-01-22 16:00:56'),
(71, 8, 1, '약속의 순간', 'POEM', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page71/800/600', '2025-05-31 20:17:48', '2025-06-28 20:17:48'),
(72, 8, 2, '약속의 순간', 'POEM', '모두가 잠든 밤, 별들이 조용히 이야기를 나누었습니다. 숲속에서 들려오는 소리에 귀를 기울였습니다. 작은 마을에 사는 아이는 매일 창밖을 바라보았습니다. 겨울이 지나고 봄이 오자 나무에 새싹이 돋았습니다. 구름 사이로 햇살이 비치자 모두가 미소지었습니다.', 'Every winter, the lake froze just enough to walk across. The fox watched them from behind a fallen tree.', NULL, '2025-06-21 20:48:47', '2025-07-18 20:48:47'),
(73, 8, 3, '비 오는 날', 'POEM', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page73/800/600', '2025-09-19 05:21:05', '2025-09-21 05:21:05'),
