(120, 12, 10, '작은 결심', 'CHAPTER', '작은 마을에 사는 아이는 매일 창밖을 바라보았습니다. 숲속에서 들려오는 소리에 귀를 기울였습니다. 함께라면 무엇이든 해낼 수 있을 것 같았습니다. 작은 실수도 함께 웃으며 넘길 수 있었습니다. 오랜 기다림 끝에 반가운 소식이 도착했습니다. 바람이 불 때마다 나뭇잎이 춤을 추듯 흔들렸습니다.', 'The lantern flickered as the wind grew stronger outside. He took a deep breath and stepped through the old gate. A soft breeze carried the smell of fresh bread through the street.', NULL, '2025-10-30 04:19:32', '2025-11-11 04:19:32'),
(121, 12, 11, '새로운 친구', 'CHAPTER', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page121/800/600', '2025-04-10 17:43:59', '2025-04-19 17:43:59'),
(122, 12, 12, '다시 만난 날', 'CHAPTER', '숲속에서 들려오는 소리에 귀를 기울였습니다. 새로운 친구를 만난 순간, 마음이 두근거렸습니다.', 'The garden was full of flowers no one remembered planting. The train pulled away just as she reached the platform. The stars seemed closer than ever that quiet night. Rain tapped gently on the roof while they slept. She found an old key hidden inside the wooden box. The little village woke up slowly under the morning light.', NULL, '2025-08-22 17:46:55', '2025-08-23 17:46:55'),
(123, 12, 13, '다시 만난 날', 'CHAPTER', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page123/800/600', '2026-01-21 20:37:11', '2026-01-24 20:37:11'),
(124, 12, 14, '비 오는 날', 'CHAPTER', '아이는 손을 흔들며 친구에게 인사했습니다. 겨울이 지나고 봄이 오자 나무에 새싹이 돋았습니다. 숲속에서 들려오는 소리에 귀를 기울였습니다.', 'The garden was full of flowers no one remembered planting. Deep in the forest, something rustled quietly among the leaves. He took a deep breath and stepped through the old gate. She found an old key hidden inside the wooden box.', NULL, '2026-06-06 06:43:02', '2026-06-07 06:43:02'),
(125, 12, 15, '비 오는 날', 'CHAPTER', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page125/800/600', '2025-07-04 19:32:08', '2025-07-07 19:32:08'),
(126, 12, 16, '약속의 순간', 'CHAPTER', '겨울이 지나고 봄이 오자 나무에 새싹이 돋았습니다.', 'The fox watched them from behind a fallen tree. The dog barked twice, then ran ahead down the path. The child looked out the window and smiled at the falling snow. Deep in the forest, something rustled quietly among the leaves. He took a deep breath and stepped through the old gate.', NULL, '2025-06-04 23:04:18', '2025-06-26 23:04:18'),
(127, 12, 17, '다시 만난 날', 'CHAPTER', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page127/800/600', '2026-03-10 23:03:58', '2026-04-09 23:03:58'),
(128, 12, 18, '작은 기적', 'CHAPTER', '숲속에서 들려오는 소리에 귀를 기울였습니다. 바람이 불 때마다 나뭇잎이 춤을 추듯 흔들렸습니다.', 'The little village woke up slowly under the morning light.', NULL, '2026-03-27 02:59:28', '2026-04-21 02:59:28'),
(129, 12, 19, '마지막 인사', 'CHAPTER', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page129/800/600', '2025-09-07 17:58:20', '2025-09-12 17:58:20'),
(130, 13, 1, '작은 결심', 'POEM', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page130/800/600', '2025-09-15 03:23:30', '2025-10-08 03:23:30'),
(131, 13, 2, '첫 만남', 'POEM', '달빛 아래에서 두 친구는 오래도록 이야기를 나누었습니다. 오랜 기다림 끝에 반가운 소식이 도착했습니다. 작은 발걸음이 모여 커다란 여행이 되었습니다. 비가 그치자 무지개가 마을을 감쌌습니다. 숲속에서 들려오는 소리에 귀를 기울였습니다.', 'The children built a small boat out of paper and leaves. Two old friends sat by the river and shared their stories. The last page of the book was missing, and no one knew why. A soft breeze carried the smell of fresh bread through the street. A warm cup of tea waited for him on the table. A single candle lit the whole room with a warm glow.', NULL, '2025-03-13 04:29:55', '2025-03-23 04:29:55'),
(132, 13, 3, '함께한 하루', 'POEM', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page132/800/600', '2025-09-17 15:20:39', '2025-10-03 15:20:39'),
(133, 13, 4, '다시 만난 날', 'POEM', '구름 사이로 햇살이 비치자 모두가 미소지었습니다. 아이는 손을 흔들며 친구에게 인사했습니다. 작은 발걸음이 모여 커다란 여행이 되었습니다. 겨울이 지나고 봄이 오자 나무에 새싹이 돋았습니다.', 'A single candle lit the whole room with a warm glow. She found an old key hidden inside the wooden box. A soft breeze carried the smell of fresh bread through the street. The child looked out the window and smiled at the falling snow.', NULL, '2026-05-12 06:49:29', '2026-06-01 06:49:29'),
(134, 13, 5, '첫 만남', 'POEM', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page134/800/600', '2026-02-06 22:45:36', '2026-02-22 22:45:36'),
(135, 13, 6, '비 오는 날', 'POEM', '비가 그치자 무지개가 마을을 감쌌습니다.', 'The stars seemed closer than ever that quiet night. Nobody in town could explain where the music came from. Nobody expected the small boat to survive the storm. Every evening, the baker left a loaf of bread by the door. The fox watched them from behind a fallen tree. The dog barked twice, then ran ahead down the path.', NULL, '2026-03-13 10:39:50', '2026-04-09 10:39:50'),
