(177, 18, 3, '함께한 하루', 'CHAPTER', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page177/800/600', '2025-06-04 02:34:02', '2025-06-28 02:34:02'),
(178, 18, 4, '비 오는 날', 'CHAPTER', '처음엔 무서웠지만 곧 용기를 내기로 했습니다. 작은 실수도 함께 웃으며 넘길 수 있었습니다.', 'Rain tapped gently on the roof while they slept. A soft breeze carried the smell of fresh bread through the street.', NULL, '2025-05-14 00:39:34', '2025-05-18 00:39:34'),
(179, 18, 5, '마지막 인사', 'CHAPTER', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page179/800/600', '2026-02-02 13:47:24', '2026-02-16 13:47:24'),
(180, 18, 6, '새로운 친구', 'CHAPTER', '비가 그치자 무지개가 마을을 감쌌습니다. 작은 발걸음이 모여 커다란 여행이 되었습니다. 처음엔 무서웠지만 곧 용기를 내기로 했습니다.', 'The child looked out the window and smiled at the falling snow. The children built a small boat out of paper and leaves.', NULL, '2025-05-23 03:57:16', '2025-06-09 03:57:16'),
(181, 18, 7, '돌아오는 길', 'CHAPTER', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page181/800/600', '2025-07-29 15:52:42', '2025-08-12 15:52:42'),
(182, 18, 8, '첫 만남', 'CHAPTER', '처음엔 무서웠지만 곧 용기를 내기로 했습니다.', 'Deep in the forest, something rustled quietly among the leaves. A soft breeze carried the smell of fresh bread through the street. The garden was full of flowers no one remembered planting. The fox watched them from behind a fallen tree. Nobody in town could explain where the music came from.', NULL, '2025-09-12 05:21:51', '2025-10-09 05:21:51'),
(183, 18, 9, '작은 결심', 'CHAPTER', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page183/800/600', '2025-06-20 19:25:19', '2025-07-15 19:25:19'),
(184, 18, 10, '다시 만난 날', 'CHAPTER', '비가 그치자 무지개가 마을을 감쌌습니다.', 'The fox watched them from behind a fallen tree. Every winter, the lake froze just enough to walk across. The mountain path was steep, but the view was worth it. The dog barked twice, then ran ahead down the path. Two old friends sat by the river and shared their stories. The stars seemed closer than ever that quiet night.', NULL, '2026-06-01 23:37:55', '2026-06-02 23:37:55'),
(185, 18, 11, '새로운 친구', 'CHAPTER', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page185/800/600', '2025-10-30 23:46:31', '2025-11-03 23:46:31'),
(186, 18, 12, '작은 기적', 'CHAPTER', '구름 사이로 햇살이 비치자 모두가 미소지었습니다.', 'The little village woke up slowly under the morning light. A warm cup of tea waited for him on the table. Rain tapped gently on the roof while they slept. Nobody in town could explain where the music came from.', NULL, '2025-08-30 04:23:31', '2025-09-29 04:23:31'),
(187, 18, 13, '숲으로', 'CHAPTER', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page187/800/600', '2026-03-24 04:50:26', '2026-03-25 04:50:26'),
(188, 19, 1, '약속의 순간', 'PAGE', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page188/800/600', '2025-09-08 11:07:08', '2025-10-04 11:07:08'),
(189, 19, 2, '작은 결심', 'PAGE', '오랜 기다림 끝에 반가운 소식이 도착했습니다. 새로운 친구를 만난 순간, 마음이 두근거렸습니다. 작은 마을에 사는 아이는 매일 창밖을 바라보았습니다. 함께라면 무엇이든 해낼 수 있을 것 같았습니다. 작은 발걸음이 모여 커다란 여행이 되었습니다. 숲속에서 들려오는 소리에 귀를 기울였습니다.', 'Every winter, the lake froze just enough to walk across. The stars seemed closer than ever that quiet night. Two old friends sat by the river and shared their stories. He took a deep breath and stepped through the old gate.', NULL, '2025-03-14 12:40:14', '2025-04-13 12:40:14'),
(190, 19, 3, '비 오는 날', 'PAGE', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page190/800/600', '2026-02-04 14:53:57', '2026-02-21 14:53:57'),
(191, 19, 4, '비 오는 날', 'PAGE', '바람이 불 때마다 나뭇잎이 춤을 추듯 흔들렸습니다. 모두가 잠든 밤, 별들이 조용히 이야기를 나누었습니다. 숲속에서 들려오는 소리에 귀를 기울였습니다.', 'Rain tapped gently on the roof while they slept. The old clock in the hallway had stopped ticking years ago. The lantern flickered as the wind grew stronger outside. The last page of the book was missing, and no one knew why. A single candle lit the whole room with a warm glow.', NULL, '2025-08-31 10:50:57', '2025-09-03 10:50:57'),
(192, 19, 5, '다시 만난 날', 'PAGE', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page192/800/600', '2025-06-06 23:11:23', '2025-06-09 23:11:23'),
(193, 19, 6, '작은 기적', 'PAGE', '구름 사이로 햇살이 비치자 모두가 미소지었습니다. 비가 그치자 무지개가 마을을 감쌌습니다. 아이는 손을 흔들며 친구에게 인사했습니다. 오랜 기다림 끝에 반가운 소식이 도착했습니다. 처음엔 무서웠지만 곧 용기를 내기로 했습니다. 달빛 아래에서 두 친구는 오래도록 이야기를 나누었습니다.', 'A soft breeze carried the smell of fresh bread through the street. A warm cup of tea waited for him on the table.', NULL, '2025-08-10 01:00:35', '2025-08-14 01:00:35'),
