(231, 22, 6, '따뜻한 저녁', 'PAGE', '작은 발걸음이 모여 커다란 여행이 되었습니다. 아이는 손을 흔들며 친구에게 인사했습니다. 처음엔 무서웠지만 곧 용기를 내기로 했습니다. 겨울이 지나고 봄이 오자 나무에 새싹이 돋았습니다.', 'A single candle lit the whole room with a warm glow. The fox watched them from behind a fallen tree.', NULL, '2026-03-07 17:01:47', '2026-03-24 17:01:47'),
(232, 22, 7, '작은 결심', 'PAGE', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page232/800/600', '2026-03-06 07:39:22', '2026-03-07 07:39:22'),
(233, 22, 8, '다시 만난 날', 'PAGE', '새로운 친구를 만난 순간, 마음이 두근거렸습니다.', 'The old clock in the hallway had stopped ticking years ago. A single candle lit the whole room with a warm glow. The child looked out the window and smiled at the falling snow. He took a deep breath and stepped through the old gate. A soft breeze carried the smell of fresh bread through the street.', NULL, '2025-08-18 01:40:20', '2025-09-06 01:40:20'),
(234, 22, 9, '약속의 순간', 'PAGE', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page234/800/600', '2026-04-03 06:58:12', '2026-04-18 06:58:12'),
(235, 22, 10, '비 오는 날', 'PAGE', '바람이 불 때마다 나뭇잎이 춤을 추듯 흔들렸습니다.', 'The child looked out the window and smiled at the falling snow. A single candle lit the whole room with a warm glow. Every evening, the baker left a loaf of bread by the door. The train pulled away just as she reached the platform.', NULL, '2026-06-10 09:33:37', '2026-06-16 09:33:37'),
(236, 22, 11, '숲으로', 'PAGE', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page236/800/600', '2025-11-10 01:28:03', '2025-12-02 01:28:03'),
(237, 22, 12, '비 오는 날', 'PAGE', '겨울이 지나고 봄이 오자 나무에 새싹이 돋았습니다. 비가 그치자 무지개가 마을을 감쌌습니다. 오랜 기다림 끝에 반가운 소식이 도착했습니다. 모두가 잠든 밤, 별들이 조용히 이야기를 나누었습니다. 숲속에서 들려오는 소리에 귀를 기울였습니다.', 'Rain tapped gently on the roof while they slept. The last page of the book was missing, and no one knew why. A warm cup of tea waited for him on the table. The little village woke up slowly under the morning light. A single candle lit the whole room with a warm glow.', NULL, '2025-10-27 17:23:28', '2025-10-28 17:23:28'),
(238, 22, 13, '첫 만남', 'PAGE', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page238/800/600', '2026-05-20 00:26:46', '2026-06-11 00:26:46'),
