(302, 27, 2, '작은 기적', 'PAGE', '작은 실수도 함께 웃으며 넘길 수 있었습니다. 작은 마을에 사는 아이는 매일 창밖을 바라보았습니다. 비가 그치자 무지개가 마을을 감쌌습니다. 함께라면 무엇이든 해낼 수 있을 것 같았습니다.', 'Rain tapped gently on the roof while they slept. Two old friends sat by the river and shared their stories.', NULL, '2026-02-23 07:25:51', '2026-03-04 07:25:51'),
(303, 27, 3, '약속의 순간', 'PAGE', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page303/800/600', '2025-03-17 08:38:40', '2025-04-02 08:38:40'),
(304, 27, 4, '작은 기적', 'PAGE', '작은 마을에 사는 아이는 매일 창밖을 바라보았습니다. 새로운 친구를 만난 순간, 마음이 두근거렸습니다.', 'A single candle lit the whole room with a warm glow. The dog barked twice, then ran ahead down the path.', NULL, '2026-03-26 19:25:59', '2026-04-20 19:25:59'),
(305, 27, 5, '돌아오는 길', 'PAGE', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page305/800/600', '2026-06-15 03:59:15', '2026-06-19 03:59:15'),
(306, 27, 6, '다시 만난 날', 'PAGE', '처음엔 무서웠지만 곧 용기를 내기로 했습니다.', 'The stars seemed closer than ever that quiet night. She held the letter close and read it one more time. Two old friends sat by the river and shared their stories. The little village woke up slowly under the morning light. Nobody expected the small boat to survive the storm.', NULL, '2026-02-02 03:57:57', '2026-02-07 03:57:57'),
(307, 27, 7, '비 오는 날', 'PAGE', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page307/800/600', '2025-06-28 05:26:09', '2025-07-04 05:26:09'),
(308, 27, 8, '함께한 하루', 'PAGE', '작은 발걸음이 모여 커다란 여행이 되었습니다. 구름 사이로 햇살이 비치자 모두가 미소지었습니다.', 'The dog barked twice, then ran ahead down the path. The train pulled away just as she reached the platform. The old clock in the hallway had stopped ticking years ago. She found an old key hidden inside the wooden box. The garden was full of flowers no one remembered planting. The stars seemed closer than ever that quiet night.', NULL, '2025-05-27 09:32:10', '2025-05-28 09:32:10'),
(309, 27, 9, '첫 만남', 'PAGE', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page309/800/600', '2026-01-22 13:34:37', '2026-01-28 13:34:37'),
