(320, 28, 2, '다시 만난 날', 'CHAPTER', '아이는 손을 흔들며 친구에게 인사했습니다. 함께라면 무엇이든 해낼 수 있을 것 같았습니다. 작은 발걸음이 모여 커다란 여행이 되었습니다. 모두가 잠든 밤, 별들이 조용히 이야기를 나누었습니다.', 'The fox watched them from behind a fallen tree. Deep in the forest, something rustled quietly among the leaves. The mountain path was steep, but the view was worth it. A soft breeze carried the smell of fresh bread through the street. The last page of the book was missing, and no one knew why. Every winter, the lake froze just enough to walk across.', NULL, '2025-05-07 19:51:24', '2025-06-01 19:51:24'),
