(396, 35, 12, '첫 만남', 'CHAPTER', '비가 그치자 무지개가 마을을 감쌌습니다. 작은 마을에 사는 아이는 매일 창밖을 바라보았습니다.', 'The train pulled away just as she reached the platform. Every evening, the baker left a loaf of bread by the door. Rain tapped gently on the roof while they slept. The lantern flickered as the wind grew stronger outside. A single candle lit the whole room with a warm glow.', NULL, '2026-03-14 02:49:59', '2026-03-17 02:49:59'),
(397, 35, 13, '돌아오는 길', 'CHAPTER', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page397/800/600', '2025-12-11 20:05:18', '2025-12-27 20:05:18'),
(398, 35, 14, '따뜻한 저녁', 'CHAPTER', '작은 실수도 함께 웃으며 넘길 수 있었습니다. 구름 사이로 햇살이 비치자 모두가 미소지었습니다. 오랜 기다림 끝에 반가운 소식이 도착했습니다. 바람이 불 때마다 나뭇잎이 춤을 추듯 흔들렸습니다.', 'The children built a small boat out of paper and leaves. The mountain path was steep, but the view was worth it. The train pulled away just as she reached the platform. She held the letter close and read it one more time. The garden was full of flowers no one remembered planting. Two old friends sat by the river and shared their stories.', NULL, '2025-04-01 09:02:48', '2025-04-28 09:02:48'),
(399, 36, 1, '첫 만남', 'CHAPTER', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page399/800/600', '2025-06-05 01:55:57', '2025-06-11 01:55:57'),
(400, 36, 2, '따뜻한 저녁', 'CHAPTER', '오랜 기다림 끝에 반가운 소식이 도착했습니다. 아이는 손을 흔들며 친구에게 인사했습니다. 겨울이 지나고 봄이 오자 나무에 새싹이 돋았습니다.', 'The fox watched them from behind a fallen tree. Two old friends sat by the river and shared their stories. Nobody expected the small boat to survive the storm. A single candle lit the whole room with a warm glow.', NULL, '2026-05-06 15:42:38', '2026-06-03 15:42:38'),
(401, 36, 3, '작은 기적', 'CHAPTER', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page401/800/600', '2026-02-08 19:00:30', '2026-02-12 19:00:30'),
(402, 36, 4, '함께한 하루', 'CHAPTER', '오랜 기다림 끝에 반가운 소식이 도착했습니다. 겨울이 지나고 봄이 오자 나무에 새싹이 돋았습니다. 작은 실수도 함께 웃으며 넘길 수 있었습니다. 작은 발걸음이 모여 커다란 여행이 되었습니다.', 'The stars seemed closer than ever that quiet night. He took a deep breath and stepped through the old gate. A warm cup of tea waited for him on the table. Rain tapped gently on the roof while they slept. Every evening, the baker left a loaf of bread by the door. Nobody expected the small boat to survive the storm.', NULL, '2025-07-08 11:21:08', '2025-08-01 11:21:08'),
(403, 36, 5, '작은 기적', 'CHAPTER', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page403/800/600', '2025-11-03 17:55:15', '2025-11-23 17:55:15'),
(404, 37, 1, '작은 기적', 'PAGE', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page404/800/600', '2025-10-19 19:43:13', '2025-11-08 19:43:13'),
(405, 37, 2, '돌아오는 길', 'PAGE', '작은 발걸음이 모여 커다란 여행이 되었습니다. 숲속에서 들려오는 소리에 귀를 기울였습니다.', 'He took a deep breath and stepped through the old gate.', NULL, '2026-02-04 12:08:29', '2026-02-12 12:08:29'),
(406, 37, 3, '새로운 친구', 'PAGE', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page406/800/600', '2025-06-29 08:17:51', '2025-07-17 08:17:51'),
(407, 37, 4, '함께한 하루', 'PAGE', '작은 마을에 사는 아이는 매일 창밖을 바라보았습니다. 비가 그치자 무지개가 마을을 감쌌습니다. 바람이 불 때마다 나뭇잎이 춤을 추듯 흔들렸습니다. 숲속에서 들려오는 소리에 귀를 기울였습니다. 아이는 손을 흔들며 친구에게 인사했습니다.', 'Every evening, the baker left a loaf of bread by the door. Two old friends sat by the river and shared their stories. She held the letter close and read it one more time. A soft breeze carried the smell of fresh bread through the street.', NULL, '2026-03-05 15:38:13', '2026-03-30 15:38:13'),
(408, 37, 5, '약속의 순간', 'PAGE', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page408/800/600', '2025-04-27 18:28:05', '2025-05-01 18:28:05'),
(409, 37, 6, '숲으로', 'PAGE', '작은 마을에 사는 아이는 매일 창밖을 바라보았습니다.', 'She found an old key hidden inside the wooden box. The child looked out the window and smiled at the falling snow. Deep in the forest, something rustled quietly among the leaves. The train pulled away just as she reached the platform. The fox watched them from behind a fallen tree.', NULL, '2026-06-25 10:19:20', '2026-07-03 09:15:31'),
(410, 37, 7, '다시 만난 날', 'PAGE', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page410/800/600', '2026-02-24 04:38:41', '2026-03-08 04:38:41'),
(411, 38, 1, '숲으로', 'PAGE', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page411/800/600', '2026-04-08 23:41:15', '2026-04-14 23:41:15'),
(412, 38, 2, '첫 만남', 'PAGE', '처음엔 무서웠지만 곧 용기를 내기로 했습니다. 달빛 아래에서 두 친구는 오래도록 이야기를 나누었습니다. 새로운 친구를 만난 순간, 마음이 두근거렸습니다. 함께라면 무엇이든 해낼 수 있을 것 같았습니다.', 'The train pulled away just as she reached the platform. The lantern flickered as the wind grew stronger outside.', NULL, '2025-03-01 07:40:30', '2025-03-29 07:40:30'),
(413, 38, 3, '숲으로', 'PAGE', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page413/800/600', '2026-04-06 20:26:45', '2026-04-12 20:26:45'),
(414, 38, 4, '약속의 순간', 'PAGE', '달빛 아래에서 두 친구는 오래도록 이야기를 나누었습니다.', 'Every winter, the lake froze just enough to walk across. The child looked out the window and smiled at the falling snow. Rain tapped gently on the roof while they slept. The old clock in the hallway had stopped ticking years ago.', NULL, '2025-02-21 14:07:56', '2025-03-13 14:07:56'),
(415, 38, 5, '함께한 하루', 'PAGE', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page415/800/600', '2025-08-13 03:09:25', '2025-09-04 03:09:25'),
