(713, 63, 1, '작은 결심', 'CHAPTER', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page713/800/600', '2025-02-22 15:12:59', '2025-03-16 15:12:59'),
(714, 63, 2, '돌아오는 길', 'CHAPTER', '모두가 잠든 밤, 별들이 조용히 이야기를 나누었습니다.', 'A soft breeze carried the smell of fresh bread through the street. The old clock in the hallway had stopped ticking years ago. A single candle lit the whole room with a warm glow. Rain tapped gently on the roof while they slept. The train pulled away just as she reached the platform. She found an old key hidden inside the wooden box.', NULL, '2025-02-23 21:52:28', '2025-03-13 21:52:28'),
(715, 63, 3, '함께한 하루', 'CHAPTER', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page715/800/600', '2026-03-29 02:19:18', '2026-03-29 02:19:18'),
(716, 63, 4, '작은 기적', 'CHAPTER', '구름 사이로 햇살이 비치자 모두가 미소지었습니다.', 'The garden was full of flowers no one remembered planting. Deep in the forest, something rustled quietly among the leaves. The stars seemed closer than ever that quiet night. Rain tapped gently on the roof while they slept. She held the letter close and read it one more time. The mountain path was steep, but the view was worth it.', NULL, '2025-07-27 22:32:26', '2025-08-18 22:32:26'),
(717, 63, 5, '첫 만남', 'CHAPTER', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page717/800/600', '2026-01-01 22:40:59', '2026-01-12 22:40:59'),
(718, 63, 6, '돌아오는 길', 'CHAPTER', '구름 사이로 햇살이 비치자 모두가 미소지었습니다. 작은 마을에 사는 아이는 매일 창밖을 바라보았습니다. 오랜 기다림 끝에 반가운 소식이 도착했습니다. 처음엔 무서웠지만 곧 용기를 내기로 했습니다.', 'Nobody expected the small boat to survive the storm. The children built a small boat out of paper and leaves. The lantern flickered as the wind grew stronger outside. The child looked out the window and smiled at the falling snow. Two old friends sat by the river and shared their stories. Nobody in town could explain where the music came from.', NULL, '2026-01-15 07:48:31', '2026-02-04 07:48:31'),
(719, 63, 7, '비 오는 날', 'CHAPTER', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page719/800/600', '2025-09-09 08:17:51', '2025-10-06 08:17:51'),
(720, 63, 8, '함께한 하루', 'CHAPTER', '숲속에서 들려오는 소리에 귀를 기울였습니다. 작은 발걸음이 모여 커다란 여행이 되었습니다. 바람이 불 때마다 나뭇잎이 춤을 추듯 흔들렸습니다.', 'The old clock in the hallway had stopped ticking years ago. The children built a small boat out of paper and leaves.', NULL, '2026-05-02 23:28:29', '2026-05-13 23:28:29'),
(721, 63, 9, '작은 결심', 'CHAPTER', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page721/800/600', '2025-12-24 02:20:27', '2026-01-17 02:20:27'),
(722, 63, 10, '작은 기적', 'CHAPTER', '비가 그치자 무지개가 마을을 감쌌습니다. 함께라면 무엇이든 해낼 수 있을 것 같았습니다. 아이는 손을 흔들며 친구에게 인사했습니다. 작은 실수도 함께 웃으며 넘길 수 있었습니다.', 'The dog barked twice, then ran ahead down the path. The mountain path was steep, but the view was worth it.', NULL, '2026-04-23 05:14:26', '2026-05-18 05:14:26'),
(723, 63, 11, '숲으로', 'CHAPTER', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page723/800/600', '2025-07-07 04:50:00', '2025-07-18 04:50:00'),
