(902, 76, 2, '돌아오는 길', 'POEM', '처음엔 무서웠지만 곧 용기를 내기로 했습니다. 작은 실수도 함께 웃으며 넘길 수 있었습니다.', 'The fox watched them from behind a fallen tree. The little village woke up slowly under the morning light. She found an old key hidden inside the wooden box. The garden was full of flowers no one remembered planting. The old clock in the hallway had stopped ticking years ago.', NULL, '2026-05-15 17:19:09', '2026-06-09 17:19:09'),
