(1180, 97, 14, '다시 만난 날', 'PAGE', '모두가 잠든 밤, 별들이 조용히 이야기를 나누었습니다. 구름 사이로 햇살이 비치자 모두가 미소지었습니다. 작은 발걸음이 모여 커다란 여행이 되었습니다.', 'A soft breeze carried the smell of fresh bread through the street. The train pulled away just as she reached the platform.', NULL, '2026-03-18 09:41:00', '2026-03-18 09:41:00'),
(1181, 97, 15, '새로운 친구', 'PAGE', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page1181/800/600', '2026-03-13 18:56:47', '2026-03-17 18:56:47'),
(1182, 97, 16, '함께한 하루', 'PAGE', '함께라면 무엇이든 해낼 수 있을 것 같았습니다. 오랜 기다림 끝에 반가운 소식이 도착했습니다. 아이는 손을 흔들며 친구에게 인사했습니다. 처음엔 무서웠지만 곧 용기를 내기로 했습니다.', 'She held the letter close and read it one more time. The last page of the book was missing, and no one knew why. The stars seemed closer than ever that quiet night. The old clock in the hallway had stopped ticking years ago. The mountain path was steep, but the view was worth it.', NULL, '2026-02-28 21:49:43', '2026-03-23 21:49:43'),
(1183, 98, 1, '첫 만남', 'CHAPTER', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page1183/800/600', '2025-10-17 10:45:51', '2025-11-10 10:45:51'),
(1184, 98, 2, '다시 만난 날', 'CHAPTER', '모두가 잠든 밤, 별들이 조용히 이야기를 나누었습니다. 함께라면 무엇이든 해낼 수 있을 것 같았습니다. 오랜 기다림 끝에 반가운 소식이 도착했습니다.', 'Every winter, the lake froze just enough to walk across. She found an old key hidden inside the wooden box.', NULL, '2025-05-05 16:48:01', '2025-05-31 16:48:01'),
(1185, 98, 3, '새로운 친구', 'CHAPTER', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page1185/800/600', '2026-03-26 06:55:44', '2026-04-16 06:55:44'),
(1186, 98, 4, '첫 만남', 'CHAPTER', '처음엔 무서웠지만 곧 용기를 내기로 했습니다.', 'The lantern flickered as the wind grew stronger outside. The child looked out the window and smiled at the falling snow. A single candle lit the whole room with a warm glow. Every evening, the baker left a loaf of bread by the door.', NULL, '2025-07-27 18:13:24', '2025-08-19 18:13:24'),
(1187, 98, 5, '새로운 친구', 'CHAPTER', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page1187/800/600', '2025-12-16 10:25:35', '2026-01-07 10:25:35'),
(1188, 98, 6, '다시 만난 날', 'CHAPTER', '새로운 친구를 만난 순간, 마음이 두근거렸습니다. 아이는 손을 흔들며 친구에게 인사했습니다.', 'The train pulled away just as she reached the platform. Nobody in town could explain where the music came from. Every evening, the baker left a loaf of bread by the door. She held the letter close and read it one more time. Rain tapped gently on the roof while they slept. The stars seemed closer than ever that quiet night.', NULL, '2025-05-19 08:35:52', '2025-05-19 08:35:52'),
(1189, 98, 7, '다시 만난 날', 'CHAPTER', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page1189/800/600', '2025-03-24 14:02:11', '2025-04-14 14:02:11'),
(1190, 98, 8, '다시 만난 날', 'CHAPTER', '겨울이 지나고 봄이 오자 나무에 새싹이 돋았습니다. 새로운 친구를 만난 순간, 마음이 두근거렸습니다. 숲속에서 들려오는 소리에 귀를 기울였습니다. 함께라면 무엇이든 해낼 수 있을 것 같았습니다.', 'A single candle lit the whole room with a warm glow. The lantern flickered as the wind grew stronger outside.', NULL, '2025-04-27 00:28:15', '2025-05-07 00:28:15'),
(1191, 98, 9, '마지막 인사', 'CHAPTER', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page1191/800/600', '2025-03-26 05:21:58', '2025-03-29 05:21:58'),
(1192, 98, 10, '작은 결심', 'CHAPTER', '새로운 친구를 만난 순간, 마음이 두근거렸습니다. 비가 그치자 무지개가 마을을 감쌌습니다.', 'A warm cup of tea waited for him on the table. Nobody expected the small boat to survive the storm. Nobody in town could explain where the music came from. The fox watched them from behind a fallen tree. The lantern flickered as the wind grew stronger outside.', NULL, '2025-10-19 02:19:22', '2025-10-19 02:19:22'),
(1193, 99, 1, '마지막 인사', 'CHAPTER', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page1193/800/600', '2025-10-18 20:01:26', '2025-11-07 20:01:26'),
