(1404, 118, 11, '작은 기적', 'CHAPTER', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page1404/800/600', '2025-04-22 02:02:13', '2025-04-22 02:02:13'),
(1405, 118, 12, '새로운 친구', 'CHAPTER', '구름 사이로 햇살이 비치자 모두가 미소지었습니다.', 'Deep in the forest, something rustled quietly among the leaves. Nobody in town could explain where the music came from. He took a deep breath and stepped through the old gate. She held the letter close and read it one more time. Every evening, the baker left a loaf of bread by the door. The garden was full of flowers no one remembered planting.', NULL, '2025-04-28 14:58:18', '2025-05-20 14:58:18'),
