(1407, 118, 14, '약속의 순간', 'CHAPTER', '작은 발걸음이 모여 커다란 여행이 되었습니다. 달빛 아래에서 두 친구는 오래도록 이야기를 나누었습니다. 겨울이 지나고 봄이 오자 나무에 새싹이 돋았습니다.', 'The mountain path was steep, but the view was worth it. The last page of the book was missing, and no one knew why. A soft breeze carried the smell of fresh bread through the street. She found an old key hidden inside the wooden box.', NULL, '2026-02-23 02:46:27', '2026-03-17 02:46:27'),
