(1490, 124, 3, '작은 결심', 'PAGE', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page1490/800/600', '2026-04-07 12:40:36', '2026-04-28 12:40:36'),
(1491, 124, 4, '첫 만남', 'PAGE', '겨울이 지나고 봄이 오자 나무에 새싹이 돋았습니다. 구름 사이로 햇살이 비치자 모두가 미소지었습니다. 오랜 기다림 끝에 반가운 소식이 도착했습니다. 아이는 손을 흔들며 친구에게 인사했습니다.', 'The old clock in the hallway had stopped ticking years ago. Every winter, the lake froze just enough to walk across. Nobody expected the small boat to survive the storm.', NULL, '2025-10-03 09:27:39', '2025-10-17 09:27:39'),
(1492, 124, 5, '작은 결심', 'PAGE', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page1492/800/600', '2025-04-10 08:38:44', '2025-04-16 08:38:44'),
(1493, 124, 6, '따뜻한 저녁', 'PAGE', '바람이 불 때마다 나뭇잎이 춤을 추듯 흔들렸습니다. 작은 발걸음이 모여 커다란 여행이 되었습니다.', 'The child looked out the window and smiled at the falling snow. The dog barked twice, then ran ahead down the path. The old clock in the hallway had stopped ticking years ago. The lantern flickered as the wind grew stronger outside. Nobody in town could explain where the music came from.', NULL, '2026-02-09 00:39:03', '2026-02-11 00:39:03'),
(1494, 124, 7, '따뜻한 저녁', 'PAGE', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page1494/800/600', '2025-07-07 06:33:09', '2025-07-16 06:33:09'),
(1495, 124, 8, '작은 결심', 'PAGE', '겨울이 지나고 봄이 오자 나무에 새싹이 돋았습니다. 새로운 친구를 만난 순간, 마음이 두근거렸습니다. 바람이 불 때마다 나뭇잎이 춤을 추듯 흔들렸습니다.', 'The dog barked twice, then ran ahead down the path. Nobody expected the small boat to survive the storm. Deep in the forest, something rustled quietly among the leaves. A single candle lit the whole room with a warm glow. The last page of the book was missing, and no one knew why.', NULL, '2025-04-19 03:39:37', '2025-04-22 03:39:37'),
(1496, 124, 9, '비 오는 날', 'PAGE', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page1496/800/600', '2025-05-16 09:32:53', '2025-06-07 09:32:53'),
(1497, 124, 10, '작은 결심', 'PAGE', '작은 발걸음이 모여 커다란 여행이 되었습니다. 겨울이 지나고 봄이 오자 나무에 새싹이 돋았습니다. 달빛 아래에서 두 친구는 오래도록 이야기를 나누었습니다.', 'The fox watched them from behind a fallen tree. Two old friends sat by the river and shared their stories.', NULL, '2025-06-15 06:44:45', '2025-07-12 06:44:45'),
(1498, 124, 11, '다시 만난 날', 'PAGE', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page1498/800/600', '2026-06-20 14:32:04', '2026-06-20 14:32:04'),
(1499, 124, 12, '작은 결심', 'PAGE', '비가 그치자 무지개가 마을을 감쌌습니다. 구름 사이로 햇살이 비치자 모두가 미소지었습니다. 아이는 손을 흔들며 친구에게 인사했습니다. 바람이 불 때마다 나뭇잎이 춤을 추듯 흔들렸습니다.', 'The garden was full of flowers no one remembered planting. The fox watched them from behind a fallen tree. The last page of the book was missing, and no one knew why. The mountain path was steep, but the view was worth it. Every winter, the lake froze just enough to walk across.', NULL, '2026-04-14 22:20:15', '2026-05-13 22:20:15'),
(1500, 124, 13, '작은 결심', 'PAGE', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page1500/800/600', '2025-11-14 16:13:10', '2025-11-27 16:13:10'),
(1501, 124, 14, '새로운 친구', 'PAGE', '비가 그치자 무지개가 마을을 감쌌습니다. 처음엔 무서웠지만 곧 용기를 내기로 했습니다. 구름 사이로 햇살이 비치자 모두가 미소지었습니다.', 'A warm cup of tea waited for him on the table. The old clock in the hallway had stopped ticking years ago. Two old friends sat by the river and shared their stories. The mountain path was steep, but the view was worth it. She held the letter close and read it one more time.', NULL, '2025-03-07 01:43:03', '2025-03-16 01:43:03'),
(1502, 124, 15, '돌아오는 길', 'PAGE', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page1502/800/600', '2025-03-07 12:03:03', '2025-04-03 12:03:03'),
(1503, 124, 16, '비 오는 날', 'PAGE', '숲속에서 들려오는 소리에 귀를 기울였습니다. 비가 그치자 무지개가 마을을 감쌌습니다. 작은 발걸음이 모여 커다란 여행이 되었습니다. 새로운 친구를 만난 순간, 마음이 두근거렸습니다. 처음엔 무서웠지만 곧 용기를 내기로 했습니다.', 'Every winter, the lake froze just enough to walk across. The little village woke up slowly under the morning light. The children built a small boat out of paper and leaves. The last page of the book was missing, and no one knew why. Nobody expected the small boat to survive the storm. The dog barked twice, then ran ahead down the path.', NULL, '2026-03-28 23:41:11', '2026-04-17 23:41:11'),
(1504, 124, 17, '함께한 하루', 'PAGE', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page1504/800/600', '2026-05-13 21:05:39', '2026-05-23 21:05:39'),
(1505, 124, 18, '함께한 하루', 'PAGE', '비가 그치자 무지개가 마을을 감쌌습니다. 모두가 잠든 밤, 별들이 조용히 이야기를 나누었습니다. 함께라면 무엇이든 해낼 수 있을 것 같았습니다. 새로운 친구를 만난 순간, 마음이 두근거렸습니다.', 'A single candle lit the whole room with a warm glow. The little village woke up slowly under the morning light. The last page of the book was missing, and no one knew why. The mountain path was steep, but the view was worth it. The stars seemed closer than ever that quiet night.', NULL, '2025-10-29 20:03:03', '2025-11-13 20:03:03'),
