(1557, 129, 4, '작은 결심', 'CHAPTER', '작은 실수도 함께 웃으며 넘길 수 있었습니다.', 'The old clock in the hallway had stopped ticking years ago.', NULL, '2025-06-04 17:45:49', '2025-06-10 17:45:49'),
