(1966, 172, 2, '작은 결심', 'POEM', '처음엔 무서웠지만 곧 용기를 내기로 했습니다. 작은 실수도 함께 웃으며 넘길 수 있었습니다.', 'Two old friends sat by the river and shared their stories. The train pulled away just as she reached the platform. The last page of the book was missing, and no one knew why. Nobody in town could explain where the music came from.', NULL, '2026-03-03 19:15:00', '2026-03-06 19:15:00'),
(1967, 172, 3, '새로운 친구', 'POEM', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page1967/800/600', '2026-03-03 19:15:00', '2026-03-06 19:15:00'),
(1968, 172, 4, '돌아오는 길', 'PAGE', '비가 그치자 무지개가 마을을 감쌌습니다. 숲속에서 들려오는 소리에 귀를 기울였습니다. 구름 사이로 햇살이 비치자 모두가 미소지었습니다.', 'The children built a small boat out of paper and leaves. He took a deep breath and stepped through the old gate. A soft breeze carried the smell of fresh bread through the street. The lantern flickered as the wind grew stronger outside.', NULL, '2026-03-03 19:15:00', '2026-03-06 19:15:00'),
(1969, 172, 5, '작은 결심', 'SCENE', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page1969/800/600', '2026-03-03 19:15:00', '2026-03-06 19:15:00'),
(1970, 172, 6, '함께한 하루', 'POEM', '달빛 아래에서 두 친구는 오래도록 이야기를 나누었습니다. 비가 그치자 무지개가 마을을 감쌌습니다. 숲속에서 들려오는 소리에 귀를 기울였습니다. 작은 실수도 함께 웃으며 넘길 수 있었습니다.', 'The garden was full of flowers no one remembered planting. The mountain path was steep, but the view was worth it. The children built a small boat out of paper and leaves. Deep in the forest, something rustled quietly among the leaves.', NULL, '2026-03-03 19:15:00', '2026-03-06 19:15:00'),
(1971, 172, 7, '따뜻한 저녁', 'CHAPTER', NULL, NULL, 'https://picsum.photos/seed/page1971/800/600', '2026-03-03 19:15:00', '2026-03-06 19:15:00'),
